  "name": "RPlog_Battle_of_Teyr_Part_1",
  "title": "Recon Over Teyr",
  "summary": "An Imperial recon flight led by Flight Officer Liza Molokai slips toward Teyr, where remnants of the anti-Vadim resistance have gathered a fleet defended by three Golan III battlestations and four Star Destroyers. Resistance commander Admiral Harkenson detects the incursion and scrambles squadrons of captured TIEs to destroy the sensor shuttle before it can escape with intelligence. Molokai's skilled Alpha Squadron shields the shuttle and shreds the attacking Green and Dagger squadrons while the shuttle pilot completes his scans of the Golans, Star Destroyers, and supporting cruisers. When Imperial corvettes arrive to cover the recon force's withdrawal, Harkenson realizes it was never an invasion and orders his guns to make the Imperials pay before breaking off, leaving him to mourn the pilots he spent on a wrong assumption.",
